  <brief_title>Surgery With or Without Chemotherapy in Treating Patients With Soft Tissue Sarcoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>RANDOMISED TRIAL OF ADJUVANT CHEMOTHERAPY WITH HIGH-DOSE DOXORUBICIN, IFOSFAMIDE AND LENOGRASTIM IN HIGH GRADE SOFT TISSUE SARCOMA</official_title>
